<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap">

    <style>

        body {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: url('../../header1-1-1536x435.jpg') center/cover no-repeat fixed;
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(17, 7, 7, 0.5);
            padding: 0px;
            width: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

            .navbar img {
                height: 77px;
                width: 680px;
                margin-left: -110px;
            }

            .navbar ul {
                list-style: none;
                display: flex;
            }


                .navbar ul li {
                    margin: 0 30px;
                    color: black;
                    font-size: 20px;
                }

                    .navbar ul li:hover {
                        color: red;
                    }

        .form-horizontal img {
            height: 107px;
            width: 150px;
            margin-left: 76px;
            margin-top: -28px;
            margin-bottom: -31px;
        }

        .card {
            width: 27rem;
            margin-top: 80px; /* Adjust the margin-top value based on your design */

            margin-left: -850px; /* Set the margin-left to position it on the left side */
            position: relative; /* Add this to make it a positioned container */
        }

        .card-img-top {
            width: 27rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(249, 249, 249, 0.5);
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: -20px;
            border-radius: 8px; /* Optional: Add border-radius for rounded corners */
        }

        .card-body h1 {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: -5px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size:x-large;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .card-body p {
       
            padding: 0px 15px;
            color:lightgrey;
            font-size: 17px;
        }
        .card:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgb(255, 215, 0);
            transition: 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        .card-body:hover{
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgb(239, 6, 6);
            transition: 1s ease;
        }
        .card-body a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #050505;
        }

        .card-body a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #ED1B24;
            padding: 10px 80px;
           
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-left: 110px;
            border: 2px solid #ED1B24;
        }

        .card-body {
            background-color: rgba(33, 33, 33, 0.7); /* Match the background color of the form */


            height: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgb(255, 255, 255);
        }

        .form-horizontal:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgb(239, 6, 6);
            transition: 1s ease;
        }

        .form-horizontal {
            max-width: 300px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            height: 440px;
            background-color: rgba(21, 21, 21, 0.7);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgb(214, 145, 145);
            margin-top: -530px;
            margin-left: 900px; /* Adjust the margin-left value based on your design */
        }


        h2,
        h4 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 35px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .control-label {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form-group {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 6px;
        }



        .form-control {
            flex: 2;
            width: calc(100% - 30px);
            padding: 10px;
            margin-left: 10px; /* Adjust margin as needed */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-default:hover {
            background-color: #030303;
            color: #ED1B24;
            transition: 0.9s ease;
        }

        .btn-default {
            background-color: #ED1B24;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 60px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-left: 64px;
            border-radius: 7px;
            border: 2px solid #ED1B24;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .forgot-password {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

            .forgot-password a {
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: underline;
                /* Smooth transition effect */
            }

                .forgot-password a:hover {
                    color: red;
                    transition: color 1s ease;
                }

        .inp {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .text-danger {
            color: #ff5e5e;
        }
    </style>

    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha512-KyZXEAg3QhqLMpG8r+Knujsl5+z0I5t9z/TNME5ZEsx4BCQkTXtk+np1Fzr1/W+MtkG6R8O3z8UJmMvktL8qGg=="
          crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />


</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <img src="~/logo.png">
        <ul>
            <li>Donations</li>
            <li>Services & Departments</li>
            <li>Join Us</li>
            <li>Doctors</li>
        </ul>
    </div>



    <div class="card">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="~/imi.png" alt="Card image cap">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="card-title">MR Imran Khan</h1>
            <p class="card-text">In December 2022, Shaukat Khanum Memorial Cancer Hospital and Research Centre in Lahore completed twenty-eight years when I was told that building and running a cancer hospital in Pakistan, where the majority of patients would be treated free of charge, was impossible. Your continuing support over the years has silenced the nay-sayers and has shown I remain more confident than ever that your generosity will enable us to open our third, and Pakistan’s largest, dedicated cancer hospital in Karachi at the end of 2023, as planned, Inshallah.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Details</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-horizontal">
        <img src="~/logo2-removebg-preview.png" alt="Logo">
        <h2>Login</h2>
        @using (Html.BeginForm())
        {
            @Html.AntiForgeryToken()


            <hr />
            @Html.ValidationSummary(true, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })

            <div class="form-group">

                <input type="text"placeholder="Username or Email" id="did"placeholder="Username or Email" name="did" class="form-control" />
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.did, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
               
                <input type="password" id="Paassword" name="Paassword" class="form-control"placeholder="Password" />
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.Paassword, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
            </div>
          

            <div class="form-group inp">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> LOGIN</button>
            </div>
            <div class="forgot-password">
                <a href="forgot-password.html">Forgot Password ?</a>
            </div>
        }
        @if (ViewBag.WelcomeMessage != null)
        {
            <h4>@ViewBag.WelcomeMessage</h4>
        }

    </div>
    @section Scripts {
        @Scripts.Render("~/bundles/jqueryval")
    }
</body>

</html>
